AutoDetectAction_actionPerformed_d_title=Configuration de reconnexion automatique
AutoDetectAction_actionPerformed_dooptimization_msg=JDownloader found %s1 working Reconnect Script(s). \n\nTo improve Reconnect Timings, you should do some automatic tests runs. These tests would take about %s2. \n\nIf you skip this step, your current Reconnect Settings will need about %s3 to perform a successful Reconnect.
